---
import SvgWrapper from '~/components/icons/SvgWrapper.astro';
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Work History">
  <h1 class="text-text-inverse text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Work History</h1>

  <!-- Teamshares Inc. -->
  <div class="flex flex-col p-2 shadow-lg rounded-lg work-history-entry bg-zinc-400">
    <div class="content-header hover:cursor-pointer">
      <div class="flex flex-row gap-2">
        <h2 class="font-medium">Senior Software Engineer @ Teamshares Inc.</h2>
        <p class="">New York, NY (Remote)</p>
        <SvgWrapper
          width={24}
          height={24}
          classes="ml-auto top-4 right-0 collapse-icon transform duration-300 ease-in-out"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
          <path
            id="Vector"
            d="M15 11L12 14L9 11"
            stroke="#000000"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
        </SvgWrapper>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm"><i>Aug 2022 - Mar 2024</i></p>
    </div>

    <div class="transition-max-height duration-500 ease-in-out overflow-hidden max-h-0 content">
      <p class="flex flex-row mt-2">
        <span class="font-medium">Mentorship & Leadership</span>:
        <p>
          Guided junior engineers in advancing their software projects using domain-driven design principles, focusing
          on innovative solutions to enhance product functionality and alignment with business goals
        </p>
      </p>

      <p class="flex flex-row mt-2">
        <span class="font-medium">Data Architecture</span>:
        <p>
          Initiated and led working sessions to redesign existing data models based on domain-driven design to
          accurately mirror business processes, significantly reducing the risk of technical debt associated with future
          system overhauls
        </p>
      </p>

      <p class="flex flex-row mt-2">
        <span class="font-medium">QA & CI/CD Optimization</span>:
        <p>
          Dedicated significant efforts to shore up both unit and end-to-end testing frameworks. Enhanced the stability
          and reliability of the CI/CD pipeline by identifying and resolving sources of flakiness in tests
        </p>
      </p>

      <p class="flex flex-row mt-2">
        <span class="font-medium">Projects / Development</span>:
        <ul class="list-disc pl-8">
          <li>
            ETL pipeline: Aggregated user equity and dividend payout data used to automate tax filing documents with
            Ruby on Rails
          </li>
          <li>
            ETL pipeline: Automated processes that executed complex business rules and eliminated human error from
            manual data entry (Zendesk data transfer, equity issuance and deferred cancelation workflow, )
          </li>
          <li>
            ETL pipeline: Automated company valuations data workflow and eliminated the need for csv files being passed
            between teams
          </li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- TempoAutomation Inc. -->
  <div class="flex flex-col p-2 shadow-lg rounded-lg work-history-entry bg-zinc-400 mt-8">
    <div class="content-header hover:cursor-pointer">
      <div class="flex flex-row gap-2">
