            stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
        </SvgWrapper>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm"><i>Apr 2021 - May 2022</i></p>
    </div>

    <div class="transition-max-height duration-500 ease-in-out overflow-hidden max-h-0">
      <p class="flex flex-row mt-2">
        <span class="font-medium">Team & Vision Leadership</span>:
        <p>
          Solely responsible for the DevOps domain on a newly formed team. Defined scope, responsibilities, and both
          short and long-term goals. Crafted a comprehensive two-year roadmap to develop core infrastructure components
          essential for organizational growth
        </p>
      </p>

      <p class="flex flex-row mt-2">
        <span class="font-medium">Strategic Audits & Planning</span>:
